        <div class="col-sm-6">

            <div class="revised-callout-content">
                    <div class="content-title">
                        Smart Cities
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-text">
                        <p> The future is being built today, and <a href="/about-us/our-company">Johnson Controls</a> is making that future more secure, more productive, and more sustainable. We create intelligent buildings, efficient energy solutions, integrated infrastructure and next generation energy storage systems that work seamlessly together to deliver on the promise of smart cities and communities. At its core, that promise is about delivering tangible solutions and innovations that make people&rsquo;s lives &mdash; and the world &mdash; better. Our commitment to sustainability dates back to our roots in 1885, with the invention of the first electric room thermostat. </p>
<p><strong>Johnson Controls&rsquo; innovative solutions are driving the future of smart cities</strong><br>
As today&rsquo;s buildings, communities and cities advance, Johnson Controls is driving the transformation to meet today&rsquo;s needs and tomorrow&rsquo;s opportunities. We combine future-focused technologies with expert insight to build connected, secure, sustainable built environments and energy solutions that move the world forward.</p>
<p><strong>Learn more</strong>:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Article:&nbsp;<a href="/insights/2017/enterprise/features/the-key-trends-making-our-cities-greener-safer-and-smarter">The key trends making our cities greener, safer and smarter</a></li>
    <li>Whitepaper:&nbsp;<a href="/insights/2017/buildings/features/cybersmart-buildings">Cybersmart buildings</a></li>
    <li>Article:&nbsp;<a href="/insights/2017/buildings/features/delivering-the-promise-of-smart-cities">Smart investment in smart cities</a></li>
</ul>
                    </div>

                <div class="content-btns">

                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pin"></div>
    </div>



    <div class="revised-image-callout-right revised-image-callout revised-callout-wrapper container">

        <div class="category col-sm-12">
            
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">

            <div class="revised-callout-content">
                    <div class="content-title">
                        Johnson Controls Hall of Fame Village
                    </div>
                
                    <div class="content-text">
                            <p><a href="http://www.jcihofv.com/">The Johnson Controls Hall of Fame Village</a> is a premier sports and entertainment destination in Canton, Ohio. The nearly $800 million &ldquo;smart city&rdquo; will provide world-class football fan experiences enabled by state-of-the-art technology products and services. </p>
<p>The village will include a museum, multi-purpose stadium, hotel, football and youth sports complex, center for excellence, performance center, player care center and an interactive, immersive virtual reality experience and water park.</p>
<p>Johnson Controls is building a "smart city" for the Hall of Fame Village, and will furnish, install and integrate the majority of systems, products, services and technology for the Hall of Fame Village. The "smart city" will be driven by advanced data and analytics, connectivity and efficiency through infrastructure integration.&nbsp;Seamless innovative technology will be driven to enhance the fan experience using analytics, machine learning and artificial intelligence.</p>
<p><strong>Learn more</strong>:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Article:&nbsp;<a href="/insights/2016/enterprise/features/football-hall-of-fame-naming-rights">Johnson Controls and Pro Football Hall of Fame Village to create first-ever sports and entertainment "smart city"</a></li>
    <li>News release:&nbsp;<a href="/media-center/news/press-releases/2017/08/03/new-johnson-controls-hall-of-fame-village-logo-will-be-a-powerful-symbol-of-the-firstever-sports-and-entertainment-smart-city">New Johnson Controls Hall Of Fame Village Logo will be a powerful symbol of the first-ever sports and entertainment "smart city"</a></li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
                    </div>
                <div class="content-btns">


                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

